            "title": "盤中速報 - 深證成指上漲242.18點至12360.8846點，漲幅2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間05日10:45，深證成指上漲242.18點（或2%），暫報12360.88點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：-3.6%</li><li>近 1 月：+9.76%</li><li>近 3 月：+19.46%</li><li>近 6 月：+13.48%</li><li>今年以來：+16.36%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鈉離子電池概念領漲+4.54%。其中    欣旺達(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300207:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300207\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300207-CN</a>)            上漲        10.04%            ;        天賜材料(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002709:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002709\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002709-CN</a>)            上漲        10.02%            ;        多氟多(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002407:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002407\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002407-CN</a>)            上漲        9.99%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鈷概念領漲+3.59%。其中    道氏技術(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300409-CN</a>)            上漲        8.84%            ;        贛鋒鋰業(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:002460:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/002460\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">002460-CN</a>)            上漲        6.81%            ;        當升科技(<a data-ga-click-item=\"CNS:300073:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/astock/quote/300073\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">300073-CN</a>)            上漲        6.11%    。</p></section></main>",
